I saw this young man rise up for a leader will be exposed and I've told you the Lord said 1 Corinthians 5:5, a major shaking's coming to the church.

00:58:47.920 --> 00:58:54.210
But I saw new Davids, new Esthers, new Annas, new Joshuas, and new Calebs.

00:58:54.210 --> 00:59:12.799
I'm talking a major move on people that have no names that will rise up seemingly out of nowhere that will have major anointings on their lives, and you're going to go, 'Where in the world did this person come from?

00:59:12.799 --> 00:59:16.787
' But I'm hearing by the spirit of God: get ready for it.

00:59:16.787 --> 00:59:26.000
There are many of you that are on the sidelines right now and you're saying, 'Coach, put me in the game.

00:59:26.000 --> 00:59:33.360
' There's only a couple more minutes in the game.

00:59:33.360 --> 00:59:41.738
He said, 'No, but I saved the best for last.

00:59:41.738 --> 00:59:51.707
' There may be two minutes in the game and you're down by one.

00:59:51.707 --> 00:59:56.488
It seems like everything's going around us.

01:00:00.328 --> 01:00:03.830
You see all the stuff going on and you're thinking, 'How are we going to win?

01:00:03.830 --> 01:00:12.686
' But God, he put our closers in and he says, 'Hey, you were built for pressure.

01:00:12.686 --> 01:00:17.680
' A great anointing is coming on his people like you wouldn't believe.

01:00:17.680 --> 01:00:29.573
I'm telling you ladies and gentlemen, it's time to expand the nets for it's not going to be catching them by poles anymore.

01:00:29.573 --> 01:00:36.559
We're going to be catching them by the nets, shrimp boat nets, remember?

01:00:36.559 --> 01:00:44.343
And we're dredging the whole river bank and we're going out in the deep waters.

01:00:44.343 --> 01:00:51.066
He's leaving the 99 to go after the one.

01:00:51.066 --> 01:00:58.640
It's time for Billy Graham type anointings to go on people to reach the lost for Jesus.

01:00:58.640 --> 01:01:02.640
It's what he cares about the most.

01:01:02.640 --> 01:01:10.469
He wants that none should perish but all come to repentance.

01:01:10.469 --> 01:01:15.173
He doesn't want any of us to go to hell.

01:01:15.173 --> 01:01:16.840
Not one of us.

01:01:25.040 --> 01:01:25.458
But you choose.

01:01:25.458 --> 01:01:30.274
Hell was made for Satan and his goons.

01:01:30.274 --> 01:01:36.400
It wasn't made for you or for me or for anybody you love.

01:01:36.400 --> 01:01:38.160
It was made for the devil.

01:01:38.160 --> 01:01:41.280
But you choose hell if you don't choose Christ.

01:01:41.280 --> 01:01:42.986
He's a gentleman.

01:01:42.986 --> 01:01:46.320
He doesn't force his way into your house.

01:01:46.320 --> 01:01:55.226
He waits to see if you seek and you'll find, knock and the door will open.

01:01:55.226 --> 01:02:02.730
But the Bible also says that no man comes to the father unless he calls him.

01:02:02.730 --> 01:02:05.303
But he's calling you right now.

01:02:15.920 --> 01:02:16.120
It's appointed unto man once to die and after that the judgment.

01:02:16.120 --> 01:02:27.820
But tonight I cannot keep going on without at least, before I go tubing, we pray to even give you an opportunity to know my friend.

01:02:30.480 --> 01:02:37.040
If you're here right now and what we said about Candace, none of that really matters compared to if you don't know him.

01:02:40.462 --> 01:02:40.764
If you die tonight, where will you spend eternity?

01:02:45.199 --> 01:02:45.999
I have to ask you that because it's the most important thing.

01:02:45.999 --> 01:02:51.325
There are so many people that are on the edge of death.

01:02:51.325 --> 01:02:53.691
170-some thousand people die every day.

01:02:59.288 --> 01:02:59.504
Will you be one of them?

01:02:59.504 --> 01:03:02.000
Could it be your time?

01:03:02.000 --> 01:03:06.890
Could your number come up tonight when you're sleeping?

01:03:06.890 --> 01:03:09.199
None of us are promised tomorrow.

01:03:15.619 --> 01:03:16.269
We're all believing for a long life.

01:03:16.269 --> 01:03:21.387
Will he satisfy us and show us his salvation?

01:03:21.387 --> 01:03:25.320
But people go home all the time and didn't expect it.

01:03:25.320 --> 01:03:30.057
My question is: where will you spend eternity if you were the one that died?

01:03:35.840 --> 01:03:36.479
I want you to really search your heart.

01:03:44.520 --> 01:03:49.760
You may say, 'I know him,' but does he know you?

01:03:49.760 --> 01:03:54.640
Unless a man is born again, he cannot enter the kingdom of God.

01:03:54.640 --> 01:03:58.373
And that's your ticket to heaven.

01:03:58.373 --> 01:04:01.790
But I want to go even further.

01:04:01.790 --> 01:04:03.890
Does he know me?

01:04:07.509 --> 01:04:08.410
You used to be born again, but you turned your back from it.

01:04:09.660 --> 01:04:16.169
You come here because it's entertaining to you maybe, but yet you feel inside you're just not living right.

01:04:19.730 --> 01:04:22.280
You might be sleeping around, you might be doing drugs, or whatever.

01:04:22.280 --> 01:04:29.280
But you went back to the vomit you said you were saved from.

01:04:35.813 --> 01:04:36.275
I want you to sell out to Jesus tonight.

01:04:39.120 --> 01:04:40.460
I want you to get radical for him tonight.

01:04:55.600 --> 01:04:56.000
He's putting in his closers.

01:04:56.000 --> 01:04:58.022
We're at the last of the last.

01:05:21.600 --> 01:05:28.560
We just got a couple more seconds on the game clock, but he knows you're able to score the winning point.

01:05:28.560 --> 01:06:00.200
He's going to use you in this end-time army.

01:06:00.200 --> 01:06:01.920
Would you help him?

01:06:01.920 --> 01:06:07.440
For the harvest is plentiful and the laborers are few.

01:06:07.440 --> 01:06:11.360
He is the Lord of the harvest.

01:06:11.360 --> 01:06:18.070
Tonight I just want to say a simple prayer with you.

01:06:18.070 --> 01:06:22.549
If you've never accepted Jesus Christ as your Lord and personal Savior, tonight's your night.

01:06:24.187 --> 01:06:28.791
I want you to put in the comment section right now, "I want to be saved.

01:06:28.791 --> 01:06:30.969
" Jesus died for you publicly.

01:06:30.969 --> 01:07:01.520
He suffered greatly so that you wouldn't have to go to hell.

01:07:01.520 --> 01:07:08.319
The least you can do is be bold about your commitment to Him, saying, "I want to be saved tonight.

01:07:08.319 --> 01:08:18.936
" Just say it in the comments.

01:08:18.936 --> 01:08:26.916
You don't have to go down in front of an altar full of people.

01:08:26.916 --> 01:08:46.229
You just have to type in the comment section right now, "I want to be saved.

01:08:53.839 --> 01:09:13.079
I want Jesus Christ as my Lord and personal Savior.

01:10:57.696 --> 01:10:57.984
" I don't want to go to hell, Brandon.

01:10:57.984 --> 01:11:06.434
If I were to die tonight, I don't know where I would go.

01:11:12.799 --> 01:11:13.239
I want Jesus, and I'd sell out to Jesus tonight.

01:11:13.679 --> 01:11:17.413
You must know, my friend, and He must know you.

01:11:17.413 --> 01:11:23.726
I want to say a simple prayer with you right now.

01:11:23.726 --> 01:11:41.154
If you're serious about your decision and serious about selling out to Him, I want to say a simple prayer with you.

01:11:41.154 --> 01:11:45.634
A five-year-old could say this and mean it with his heart.

01:11:45.634 --> 01:11:47.919
It's not complicated.

01:11:47.919 --> 01:11:52.034
We make it complicated.

01:11:52.034 --> 01:11:58.066
Religion makes it complicated.

01:13:37.040 --> 01:13:37.404
I cannot stand religion; I'm all about relationship.

01:13:39.591 --> 01:13:39.956
I just want Jesus.

01:13:39.956 --> 01:13:53.315
So say, "Jesus, I believe You're the Son of God.

01:14:32.031 --> 01:14:32.207
I believe You died for me and You rose again on the third day.

01:14:32.207 --> 01:14:35.269
Jesus, I'm a sinner and I need a Savior.

01:14:35.269 --> 01:14:48.800
I ask You to forgive me of my sins.

01:14:48.800 --> 01:15:18.016
Forgive me right now.

01:15:18.016 --> 01:15:21.848
I need You to forgive me.

01:15:21.848 --> 01:15:51.348
I've messed up so many times, but I know that if I confess my sins, You're faithful and just to forgive me of my sins and cleanse me of all unrighteousness.

01:15:51.348 --> 01:16:03.060
That's what Your word says.

01:16:03.060 --> 01:16:20.400
So, as of tonight, I turn my back on the world.

01:16:20.720 --> 01:16:31.759
I turn my back on the devil.

01:17:17.040 --> 01:17:17.432
I turn my back on my sin.

01:17:19.392 --> 01:17:27.306
And today, Lord, I serve You from this day forward.

01:17:27.306 --> 01:17:39.387
I sell out to You, Lord, and I ask You, Lord, to make me a new creature created in Christ Jesus.

01:17:39.387 --> 01:17:43.451
Write my name in the Lamb's Book of Life.

01:17:43.451 --> 01:18:28.550
From this day forward, Lord, I belong to You.

01:18:28.560 --> 01:18:58.640
Help me to become a better person.

01:18:58.640 --> 01:19:09.960
Help me, Lord, from day to day to seek You daily and I will find You.

01:19:12.400 --> 01:19:16.080
I want to be more like You in Jesus' name.

01:19:16.080 --> 01:19:17.360
Amen.

01:19:17.360 --> 01:19:20.590
" That's it.

01:19:20.590 --> 01:19:29.253
I believe if you said that prayer, you just gave your heart to Jesus.

01:19:37.280 --> 01:19:37.973
The best is yet to come.

01:19:51.634 --> 01:20:00.310
You just made the greatest decision you could ever make, and we rejoice with you.

01:20:08.400 --> 01:20:08.720
I don't know how many people did that, but we pray a lot of you did.

01:20:23.296 --> 01:20:23.888
We had 40 salvations.

01:20:23.888 --> 01:20:26.930
All glory to Jesus.

01:20:26.930 --> 01:20:39.010
So we pray that the Lord touched you and that you got born again.

01:20:39.010 --> 01:20:50.320
For any other stragglers from now on that watch this video, we're excited you're here.

01:20:50.320 --> 01:20:51.954
They just straggle behind.

01:20:51.954 --> 01:20:55.520
So, what do you do?

01:21:16.970 --> 01:21:17.160
I want you to read your Bible and pray every single day.

01:21:17.160 --> 01:21:19.516
Find a Bible-believing church.

01:21:22.520 --> 01:21:26.719
A non-denominational one is the one I would go to; go get plugged in there.

01:21:26.719 --> 01:22:05.595
Tell the pastor of that church, "Hey, I got born again watching a YouTube video and I need to be water-baptized.

01:22:05.595 --> 01:22:14.128
" Get plugged in there.

01:22:14.128 --> 01:22:16.816
Read your Bible.

01:22:16.816 --> 01:22:20.773
Come pray with us.

01:22:20.773 --> 01:22:23.600
And that's basically the Christian life.

01:22:23.600 --> 01:22:24.320
It's easy.

01:22:24.320 --> 01:22:31.565
Start telling people about what happened: "Jesus saved me.

01:22:31.565 --> 01:22:38.496
" He saved me from all this.

01:22:38.496 --> 01:22:43.480
I'm a new creature created in Christ Jesus.

01:22:43.480 --> 01:22:47.279
Behold, He makes all things new.

01:22:47.279 --> 01:22:58.340
So, if you don't have a Bible, Diana and I would love to buy you your first Bible for free.

01:22:58.340 --> 01:23:05.674
We want to buy it for you.

01:23:05.674 --> 01:23:28.777
If you would just go down into the description, you'll find our email.

01:23:28.777 --> 01:24:21.389
Go into the description and you'll see our email address, and in the subject line, just put "I need a Bible" and then put your name and your address in the email and we will get one to you.

01:24:29.680 --> 01:24:29.920
The angels in heaven are celebrating.

01:24:29.920 --> 01:24:35.995
We're all celebrating the 40 people who gave their hearts to Jesus Christ tonight.

01:25:01.200 --> 01:25:01.600
The best day of your life, the best decision you've ever made.

01:25:01.600 --> 01:25:08.660
For all 5,900 of you, let's pray and let's go tubing.

01:25:35.600 --> 01:25:35.920
But I give the altar call in the middle now because everybody leaves at the end, and I give the altar call, and now you still want to go tubing and you're here.

01:25:35.920 --> 01:25:37.792
It's important.

01:25:37.792 --> 01:25:43.947
You've got to stick around and we've got to pray for these unbelievers.

01:25:43.947 --> 01:25:49.232
There was such a pull for it in the spirit.

01:25:49.232 --> 01:26:00.180
I felt there are so many people that need Jesus and we've got to be patient with the babies there.

01:26:00.180 --> 01:26:14.051
He said, "Be patient with My babies," because you were a baby once and people were patient with you.

01:26:14.051 --> 01:26:28.819
They're coming in from all over the world, but we've got to give them time to get Jesus.

01:26:45.840 --> 01:26:46.380
That's all that matters.

01:26:46.380 --> 01:26:53.333
Why are we here?

01:27:22.767 --> 01:27:23.312
To get the lost.

01:27:23.312 --> 01:27:26.089
So, Father, we just thank You.

01:27:26.089 --> 01:27:43.897
Father, if You have anything to show us or tell us, we're here.

01:27:58.239 --> 01:27:58.746
I plead the blood over my spiritual eyes.

01:28:11.280 --> 01:28:11.893
I thank You, Lord, that I'm uninterrupted and unhindered by any satanic or demonic force.

01:28:11.893 --> 01:28:20.492
Father, I thank You, Lord, that You speak through my vocal cords and think through my mind.

01:28:20.492 --> 01:28:25.085
None of me and all of You in Jesus' name.

01:28:25.085 --> 01:28:39.467
I plead the blood over my eyes, Father, that I hear You, and a stranger's voice I will not follow.

01:28:39.467 --> 01:28:43.679
Anything You want to show me, we give You praise, Father.

01:28:45.600 --> 01:28:50.960
It was so interesting in the vein of that earlier, wasn't it?

01:28:50.960 --> 01:29:00.104
While he was talking, you could feel the presence and the shift for salvation.

01:29:00.944 --> 01:29:05.147
And then the Lord said, "Now you can pray.

01:29:10.516 --> 01:29:11.011
" But I'm like, "Where do you go from that, Lord?

01:29:11.011 --> 01:29:12.373
" Lord, we thank You.

01:29:12.373 --> 01:29:13.840
I see a red button.

01:29:54.320 --> 01:29:55.840
It looks like the nuclear button.

01:29:55.840 --> 01:30:06.736
It's in a briefcase-like thing and the red button is on a flat part right here in the middle.

01:30:06.736 --> 01:30:21.750
It looks like something you would push, and I see it opened up with metal all around it.

01:30:34.240 --> 01:30:34.453
I see South Korea and I see Taiwan.

01:30:34.453 --> 01:30:37.299
He's talking about South Korea and Taiwan.

01:30:37.299 --> 01:30:42.320
I have more here concerning Taiwan and what it's doing in Asia.

01:30:42.320 --> 01:30:44.320
And I see North Korea.

01:30:53.679 --> 01:30:54.399
I see North Korea and I see Kim.

01:30:57.280 --> 01:30:59.560
I heard "Cold War, but much colder.

01:30:59.560 --> 01:31:02.491
" Cold War, but much colder.

01:31:02.491 --> 01:31:04.617
Now I see the dance.

01:31:04.617 --> 01:31:14.697
I'm going to say that the praying in the spirit and a brand new tongue, letting the dance flow through you...

01:31:14.697 --> 01:31:19.840
I'm holding the vision and I want you to keep praying into it.

01:31:19.840 --> 01:31:26.440
Teaching the people to pray into it—not just seeing stuff.

01:31:26.440 --> 01:31:28.960
Praying into it is what He said.

01:31:28.960 --> 01:31:32.760
Not everybody's going to see stuff.

01:31:32.760 --> 01:31:36.370
Pray without having to see stuff.

01:31:50.622 --> 01:31:50.880
What are you wanting to pray into?

01:32:03.720 --> 01:32:03.936
A Cold War that's much colder.

01:32:03.936 --> 01:32:07.931
That's the guideline I'm trying to tell y'all.

01:32:14.194 --> 01:32:14.789
He said, "Pray without having to see something.

01:32:14.789 --> 01:32:16.571
Just pray.

01:32:16.571 --> 01:32:19.440
Let the Spirit move through your tongue.

01:32:19.440 --> 01:32:24.339
" Every time you say, "I see the shaking in the church.

01:32:30.970 --> 01:32:31.320
I see the shaking.

01:32:35.394 --> 01:32:35.840
" You must learn your authority.

01:32:37.800 --> 01:32:42.469
You must come up higher and know your authority.

01:32:44.526 --> 01:32:45.794
That's part of what he was saying.

01:32:45.794 --> 01:32:50.266
I heard it right there out of my tongues.

01:32:50.266 --> 01:32:57.920
He said, "You must know your authority.

01:32:57.920 --> 01:33:02.140
Come up higher.

01:33:02.140 --> 01:33:03.794
Come up higher.

01:33:07.040 --> 01:33:07.240
" You must know your authority.

01:33:12.400 --> 01:33:12.853
You must know who you are in Him to survive the time.

01:33:12.853 --> 01:33:16.293
But He's never given you a spirit of fear.

01:33:19.120 --> 01:33:19.360
You're never to fear.

01:33:19.360 --> 01:33:21.350
Perfect love casteth out all fear.

01:33:21.350 --> 01:33:24.000
Lord, I see the Olympics again.

01:33:24.000 --> 01:33:27.220
I see the opening ceremony.

01:33:28.240 --> 01:33:31.350
It marks a time and a place in Europe.

01:33:31.350 --> 01:33:37.293
It marks a place in Europe in time for what they summon.

01:33:37.293 --> 01:33:38.940
Clearly, you will see a shaking.

01:33:40.449 --> 01:33:42.708
I see an arm come out, and it's ripped like muscles, a very chiseled arm.

01:33:42.708 --> 01:33:50.368
It's a hand and just this part of the arm, and it came out and grabbed a hold in Rome.

01:33:52.020 --> 01:33:52.650
It grabbed a hold in Rome, Paris, and others.

01:33:55.631 --> 01:33:55.967
It will make an image.

01:33:55.967 --> 01:34:02.480
Going back to the 1920s and 30s farm life, I see overalls on a man.

01:34:15.199 --> 01:34:15.579
They're sitting at a table again as a family unit.

01:34:17.563 --> 01:34:25.160
I see them sitting around an old wooden table made of what looks like fence panels—a makeshift table—but they're giving grace and holding hands.

01:34:25.160 --> 01:34:28.910
Go back to family values.

01:34:28.910 --> 01:34:37.920
Go back to the old way of thinking, of the family core values, eating around a table as a family.

01:34:37.920 --> 01:34:56.498
An old farmer has overalls on, just an old farmer out in a garden, not the hustle and bustle.

01:34:56.498 --> 01:35:04.560
I see them all around this table, and they're giving thanks and giving grace.

01:35:04.560 --> 01:35:46.639
It's interesting; we went from the Olympics, a stance for the end times, but the church is going back to core values, back to the ABCs, as the antichrist makes his stance and the evil of their agenda.

01:35:50.320 --> 01:35:56.240
The church goes back to what matters: family core values.

01:36:54.887 --> 01:36:55.629
That's where the unit is; that's where prayer is; that's where the flow and the anointing is.

01:37:08.090 --> 01:37:08.400
A dad just being a dad, teaching his kids prayer, eating around the table.

01:37:08.400 --> 01:37:09.863
It's been lost.

01:37:09.863 --> 01:37:19.440
I heard the Spirit of the Lord say it's been lost—training up a child in the way they should go.

01:37:19.440 --> 01:37:21.040
Do you understand?

01:37:25.579 --> 01:37:25.799
He had their attention during the Great Depression.

01:37:25.799 --> 01:37:31.280
That's why I said the 30s and the late 20s.

01:37:56.864 --> 01:37:58.125
Be appreciative of what you have, for it can be taken away just like that.

01:37:58.125 --> 01:38:23.104
I hear the Spirit of the Lord say it can disappear overnight.

01:38:23.104 --> 01:38:25.822
Everything can tumble down.

01:38:25.822 --> 01:38:32.559
Be appreciative in this Thanksgiving season; give thanks for what you have.

01:38:32.559 --> 01:38:38.033
Go back to the core values of the family.

01:38:38.033 --> 01:38:51.458
Go back to giving thanks around the table.

01:38:51.458 --> 01:39:04.457
Thank you for all that You have provided for me, Lord, for it can be taken away just like that.

01:39:04.457 --> 01:39:08.536
He's taking you back to the ABCs.

01:39:08.536 --> 01:39:10.800
Carry on, He said.

01:39:10.800 --> 01:39:57.333
I see drought and a Dust Bowl.

01:39:57.333 --> 01:40:14.027
There has been a spiritual drought upon the land.

01:40:14.027 --> 01:40:19.920
This is not just a natural drought; it is a spiritual drought.

01:40:42.639 --> 01:40:42.923
I see fields where nothing is growing because it's dead.

01:40:42.923 --> 01:40:44.625
That's what's across America.

01:40:44.625 --> 01:40:54.823
Even the trees have lost their leaves, yet you pretend to be in plenty.

01:40:54.823 --> 01:41:02.432
Go back to what I had in store for family values.

01:41:07.973 --> 01:41:08.347
You want different fruit as a nation, but you must change the root.

01:41:12.320 --> 01:41:12.659
The fruit is a result of the root.

01:41:12.659 --> 01:41:16.240
That's what the Spirit of the Lord says.

01:41:16.240 --> 01:41:20.487
Go back to the foundation, the ABCs.

01:41:34.537 --> 01:41:35.074
The drought is upon the land because you stopped doing the ABCs.

01:41:35.074 --> 01:41:37.223
Discipline your children.

01:41:37.223 --> 01:41:42.120
Train up a child in the way he should go.

01:41:42.120 --> 01:41:45.893
Spare the rod and spoil the child.

01:41:45.893 --> 01:41:48.940
It didn't say beat the child, but there's discipline.

01:41:50.286 --> 01:41:50.457
It's all fundamentals.

01:41:51.120 --> 01:41:54.480
To be a champion, you must go back to the fundamentals of Christianity.

